{{italicstitle}} {{Notability|date=October 2015}} '''''Terra pericolosa''''' is an [[Italian language|Italian]] [[phrase]] for "dangerous land", used in [[cartography]] to denote regions that are believed to be likely to put the travellers in jeopardy. Such regions would probably not have been mapped or documented fully.
